data.description: Great location within highly sought after Vista Cove Condominiums for this bright, ground floor unit with easy access. See the video walkthrough and feel like you are there: https://youtu.be/WywgEal8hzQ. Open floor plan with beautiful wood engineered floors in the living area. White kitchen overlooks dining and living area that is perfect for entertaining or easy living. Split bedroom plan has spacious primary suite and ensuite bath with two walk-in closets, dual sinks and soaker tub-shower combination. The guest wing, set apart by a door for ultimate privacy, includes two bedrooms, one with a spacious walk-in closet providing ample space for excess storage, and a guest bathroom. Laundry room off the kitchen doubles as a pantry and there is an additional storage closet off the lanai. End the day relaxing on your screened lanai or enjoy the view of the San Sebastian River at the back of the building. You will love being a part of this amazing community with so many amenities to enjoy including the clubhouse, two pools, spa, fitness center, fishing pier, picnic area, walking trails, and the free RV/Boat storage lot. Roofs of all buildings have been recently replaced! The view from the pier is gorgeous and worth the visit and the landscaping throughout the community is just beautiful as you use the paths and walkways. Get togethers at the clubhouse helps in making new friends. Newer a/c installed 7/2021,and hot water heater installed 5/2022, both with 6 year warranties, is a plus. New glass in all windows makes it so light and bright! Just a few minutes to Historic downtown St. Augustine to enjoy restaurants and tourist stops, or the beach for beautiful views and getting your toes in the sand!
